  "detailed_description": "Crimsonwood is a roguelight top-down shooter in a cursed national park. Collect weapons, gain perks and battle hordes of enemies to remove the curse. Every run reshapes the park, offering new challenges.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/2a91f832f259e8e07f1be2982c1d63b8.poster.avif?t=1741456843\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/2a91f832f259e8e07f1be2982c1d63b8.webm?t=1741456843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/2a91f832f259e8e07f1be2982c1d63b8.mp4?t=1741456843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ARSENAL OF DESTRUCTION</h2>Discover and wield a vast array of weapons, from classic firearms to bizarre, bonemade armaments. Each weapon brings a unique strategy to the battlefield.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/30418a3007aae6354dad1b3046d80d9a.poster.avif?t=1741456843\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/30418a3007aae6354dad1b3046d80d9a.webm?t=1741456843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/30418a3007aae6354dad1b3046d80d9a.mp4?t=1741456843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PERKS</h2>Unlock and combine powerful perks to create your own playstyle. Will you focus on speed, firepower, or survivability?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/6856f420e97a6c123a804ebdcef220f1.poster.avif?t=1741456843\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/6856f420e97a6c123a804ebdcef220f1.webm?t=1741456843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/6856f420e97a6c123a804ebdcef220f1.mp4?t=1741456843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CURSED NATIONAL PARK</h2>Explore a once-peaceful park turned into a nightmarish battleground. Navigate through procedurally generated levels filled with corrupted landmarks and hidden dangers.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/52df4580f81959d0499ee21137b1a31d.poster.avif?t=1741456843\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/52df4580f81959d0499ee21137b1a31d.webm?t=1741456843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/52df4580f81959d0499ee21137b1a31d.mp4?t=1741456843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HORDES OF ENEMIES</h2>Face off against waves of corrupted creatures, each with their own attack patterns and weaknesses. From possessed park rangers to mutated wildlife, danger lurks around every corner.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/dabe6ab582530f6e509bd8303d27a4df.poster.avif?t=1741456843\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/dabe6ab582530f6e509bd8303d27a4df.webm?t=1741456843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/dabe6ab582530f6e509bd8303d27a4df.mp4?t=1741456843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Get ready to lock, load, and face hordes of enemies.<br>Crimsonwood awaits!",
  "about_the_game": "Crimsonwood is a roguelight top-down shooter in a cursed national park. Collect weapons, gain perks and battle hordes of enemies to remove the curse. Every run reshapes the park, offering new challenges.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/2a91f832f259e8e07f1be2982c1d63b8.poster.avif?t=1741456843\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/2a91f832f259e8e07f1be2982c1d63b8.webm?t=1741456843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/2a91f832f259e8e07f1be2982c1d63b8.mp4?t=1741456843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ARSENAL OF DESTRUCTION</h2>Discover and wield a vast array of weapons, from classic firearms to bizarre, bonemade armaments. Each weapon brings a unique strategy to the battlefield.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/30418a3007aae6354dad1b3046d80d9a.poster.avif?t=1741456843\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/30418a3007aae6354dad1b3046d80d9a.webm?t=1741456843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/30418a3007aae6354dad1b3046d80d9a.mp4?t=1741456843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PERKS</h2>Unlock and combine powerful perks to create your own playstyle. Will you focus on speed, firepower, or survivability?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/6856f420e97a6c123a804ebdcef220f1.poster.avif?t=1741456843\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/6856f420e97a6c123a804ebdcef220f1.webm?t=1741456843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/6856f420e97a6c123a804ebdcef220f1.mp4?t=1741456843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CURSED NATIONAL PARK</h2>Explore a once-peaceful park turned into a nightmarish battleground. Navigate through procedurally generated levels filled with corrupted landmarks and hidden dangers.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/52df4580f81959d0499ee21137b1a31d.poster.avif?t=1741456843\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/52df4580f81959d0499ee21137b1a31d.webm?t=1741456843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/52df4580f81959d0499ee21137b1a31d.mp4?t=1741456843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HORDES OF ENEMIES</h2>Face off against waves of corrupted creatures, each with their own attack patterns and weaknesses. From possessed park rangers to mutated wildlife, danger lurks around every corner.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/dabe6ab582530f6e509bd8303d27a4df.poster.avif?t=1741456843\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/dabe6ab582530f6e509bd8303d27a4df.webm?t=1741456843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/dabe6ab582530f6e509bd8303d27a4df.mp4?t=1741456843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Get ready to lock, load, and face hordes of enemies.<br>Crimsonwood awaits!",
